description:
ARK Survival Evolved is a game that takes you back to the age of the dinosaurs. You need to look for materials, hunt for food, build shelter, and discover new technology to help you conquer the elements. 

You will develop a love / hate relationship with the other creatures on the island. While many of them may try to eat you, you can also tame them to have them fight on your side.
